  "title": "Sales Associate / Senior Sales Associate (Luxury Brand) | up $3.8K + Incentives",
  "description": "<p>Description</p>\n<p>We are looking for <strong>dynamic and polished Sales Associates</strong> to join our luxury retail team at prime locations in Singapore. If you have a passion for high-end fashion or watches, enjoy interacting with customers, and thrive in a fast-paced environment, this is the perfect opportunity for you!</p>\n<p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Provide exceptional customer service, ensuring a personalized and memorable shopping experience</li>\n  <li>Advise clients on product features, trends, and styling and technical details (watches)</li>\n  <li>Achieve and exceed sales targets, upselling and cross-selling when appropriate</li>\n  <li>Maintain visual merchandising standards, ensuring product displays are clean, attractive, and aligned with brand aesthetics</li>\n  <li>Assist with inventory management, stock replenishment, and accurate record-keeping</li>\n  <li>Handle customer inquiries, complaints, and follow-ups professionally</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with team members and management to drive store performance and customer satisfaction</li>\n  <li>Participate in promotional campaigns, events, and product launches as required</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Preferred Skills &amp; Attributes:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Presentable, confident, and outgoing personality</li>\n  <li>Excellent communication and interpersonal skills</li>\n  <li>Strong interest in luxury fashion or watches</li>\n  <li>Professional, proactive, and solution-oriented</li>\n  <li>Relevant retail experience in luxury brands is highly preferred</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Why Join Us?</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Work in prestigious locations with high-end clientele</li>\n  <li>Gain valuable experience in luxury retail</li>\n  <li>Dynamic and supportive work environment</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Please send your resume in MS Word format to <strong>deborah@crew.sg</strong>, along with your availability, current salary, and last drawn salary.<br>\n<br>\nHo Yu Qing Deborah (R1104551)<br>\nCrew by HRnet | HRnet Ventures Pte Ltd<br>\nEA24C2435</p>",
